{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetagcomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTagComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent03TagB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeTagComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for tag component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the tag component tokens you want.","","        override var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken  { borders.radiusNone }","","        override var sizeMinWidthMedium: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._500 }","","        override var spacePaddingInlineIconStartSmall: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineMedium }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: TagComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(tag: CustomTagComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(tag: CustomTagComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let tagComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, space, _ and border semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let tagComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider,","                                            dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of tag","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tag","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"TagComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"tex